name: vote for the ezquisofrenico cat
description:
In a new world of joys and parties, the ezquisofrenico kitten comes from another planet, he just wants to do good but sometimes his patience runs out, as for example with the clown Milton who raped a butterfly, that's why the cat did him justice . The ezquisphrenic cat wants to be the new mayor of this planet called Grecolandia, by picking it up you are helping him with a vote, so that every Wednesday there is a new adventure of the ezquisphrenic cat.
3000x3500px
by @ZanardiGrego
